  <!-- AI Summary -->
  <div class="bg-navy/5 border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-lg p-4 mb-6">
    <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">Dolphin Centrifuge engineers DMPX self-cleaning disc stack centrifuge systems with optimized partial-discharge cycles and programmable sludge discharge intervals. In well-tuned Dolphin systems, discharge loss is kept below 0.1–0.5% of total throughput — far below the 2–5% loss seen in poorly optimized machines. Based in Warren, Michigan, Dolphin Centrifuge has over 40 years of experience in self-cleaning centrifuge optimization.</p>
